  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/11oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,44,"John D. Amos, Jay D. Andersen, Faapito Auapaau, Frederick K. Balli, Steven C. Barlow, Kevin W. Birch, John W. Boswell, Kevin G. Brown, J. Francisco Bührer, Suchat Chaichana, Christian C. Chigbundu, Matthew R. Clarke, L. Guido Cristobal, B. Corey Cuvelier, Edmarc R. Dumas, Brik V. Eyre, Timothy L. Farnes, Carlos A. Gabaldón, M. Andrew Galt, Vladislav Y. Gornostaev, Aaron T. Hall, Thomas Hänni, Richard I. Heaton, Broc C. Hiatt, Brian J. Holmes, David H. Huntsman, Norman Insong, Daniel Kabason, Federico M. Kähnlein, Jeffrey J. Kerr, David G. LaFrance, Marcelo Louza, Jose G. Manarin, Jeremiah J. Morgan, Mark A. Mortensen, S. Ephraim Msane, R. Pepper Murray, Eduardo F. Ortega, Nathan D. Pace, Michael M. Packer, Jorge W. Pérez, Kyrylo Pokhylko, Sergio A. Poncio, Art Rascon, Miguel A. Reynoso, Gustavo G. Rezende, Robert G. Rivarola, Edward B. Rowe, Alexey V. Samaykin, Luciano Sankari, Henry Savstrom, J. Matthew Scott, James E. Slaughter, Robert T. Smith, Ricardo Spencer, Colin C. Stauffer, David C. Stewart, Konstantin Tolomeev, Arlen M. Tumaliuan, Martin J. Turvey, Yan Carlos Vega, Paul B. Whippy, Chad R. Wilkinson, Dow R. Wilson, Markus Zarse."
