  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/14johnson,President Camille N. Johnson,78,"3 Nephi 12:14–16."
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/14johnson,President Camille N. Johnson,79,"In the words of the hymn:"
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/14johnson,President Camille N. Johnson,80,"This little light of mine, I’m gonna let it shine. …"
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/14johnson,President Camille N. Johnson,81,"Ev’rywhere I go, I’m gonna let it shine. …"
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/14johnson,President Camille N. Johnson,82,Jesus gave it to me; I’m gonna let it shine.
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/14johnson,President Camille N. Johnson,83,"Let it shine, let it shine, let it shine."
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/14johnson,President Camille N. Johnson,84,"(“This Little Light of Mine,”Hymns—For Home and Church, Gospel Library.)"
