  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/14johnson,President Camille N. Johnson,89,"Philippians 4:4; see also2 Corinthians 1:3–4: “Blessed be God, even the Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, the Father of mercies, and the God of all comfort; who comforteth us in all our tribulation, that we may be able to comfort them which are in any trouble, by the comfort wherewith we ourselves are comforted of God.”"
