  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/23palmer,Elder S. Mark Palmer,40,"See Dieter F. Uchtdorf, “Nourish the Roots, and the Branches Will Grow,”Liahona, Nov. 2024, 102: “Jesus Christ and His atoning sacrifice are the root of our testimony. All other things are branches. … When it comes to nourishing our testimonies of Jesus Christ, I wonder if we sometimes mistake the branches for the roots. … Nourish the roots, and the branches will grow.”"
