  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/23palmer,Elder S. Mark Palmer,43,"See also Russell M. Nelson, “Rejoice in the Gift of Priesthood Keys,”Liahona, May 2024, 122: “Here is my promise. Nothing will help youmoreto hold fast to the iron rod than worshipping in the temple. … Nothing will bolster your testimony of the Lord Jesus Christ and His Atonement or help you understand God’s magnificent planmore.”"
