  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/23palmer,Elder S. Mark Palmer,46,"See Patrick Kearon, “God’s Intent Is to Bring You Home,”Liahona, May 2024, 87: “God is in relentless pursuit of you.”"
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/23palmer,Elder S. Mark Palmer,47,"See Jeffrey R. Holland, “Broken Things to Mend,”EnsignorLiahona, May 2006, 69–71."
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/23palmer,Elder S. Mark Palmer,48,"SeeLuke 15:11–32;Doctrine and Covenants 18:13."
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/23palmer,Elder S. Mark Palmer,49,"SeeJohn 15:9."
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/23palmer,Elder S. Mark Palmer,50,"SeeAlma 5:33."
  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/23palmer,Elder S. Mark Palmer,51,"See Russell M. Nelson, “The Lord Jesus Christ Will Come Again,”Liahona, Nov. 2024, 122: “It is neither too early nor too late for you to become a devout disciple of Jesus Christ. Then you will experience fully the blessings of His Atonement.”"
