  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/24roman,Elder Sandino Roman,48,"President Gordon B. Hinckley taught, “Pray to your Heavenly Father in the name of the Lord Jesus Christ, and always, under all circumstances, by the very nature of your lives show your loyalty and your love” (“Loyalty,”EnsignorLiahona, May 2003, 60; see also Brent J. Schmidt,Relational Faith: The Transformation and Restoration of Pistis as Knowledge, Trust, Confidence, and Covenantal Faithfulness[2022], 9; Teresa Morgan,Roman Faith and Christian Faith: Pistis and Fides in the Early Roman Empire and Early Churches[2015], 127–28)."
