  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/42shumway,Elder Steven D. Shumway,47,"See Russell M. Nelson, “What We Are Learning and Will Never Forget,”Liahona, May 2021, 79: “God wants us to work together and help each other. That is why He sends us to earth in families and organizes us into wards and stakes. That is why He asks us to serve and minister to each other. … We can accomplish so much more together than we can alone. God’s plan of happiness would be frustrated if His children remained isolated one from another.”"
