  2025,"04",/general-conference/2025/04/42shumway,Elder Steven D. Shumway,67,"InJacob 1:17, 19, Jacob’s errand was the Lord’s errand. He did not magnify his office unto himself but unto the Lord so that he could teach God’s word and thus “be found spotless at the last day.”"
